	-- List of Lists skeletons;
	-- List of Lists timestamps;
	
	*load vicon file & create vicon skeletons.				---------[MARK]--------
	  .. input- path
	  .. output - list vicon skeletons
	
	*for each shooting angle (front\side\back) 				---------[MARK]--------
	  .. input - path, orientation 
	  .. output - list OpenPoseSkeleton, list timestamps
		
		load bag file.
		read bag file + create openpose skeletons + ||save list of timestamps||.
		 
	*sync openpose and vicon								---------[NOY]---------
	  .. input -  list OpenPoseSkeleton, list timestamps, list Vicon skeletons
	  .. output - list OpenPoseSkeleton, list timestamps, list Vicon skeletons
	
	*calculate measurements(knee angle.. hip.. shoulder.. according to exercise) (*check - remove    skeleton[i] & timestamps[i])							 ---------[MARK]--------
	  .. input - flag, list OpenPoseSkeleton, list timestamps
	  .. output -  list measurements, list cutTimestamps
	  
	
	*calculate measurements from VICON.						---------[MARK]-------- 
	  .. input - flag, list viconSkeletons
	  .. output - list measurements,
	
	* matching frames between openpose and vicon. 			---------[NOY]---------
	  .. input - measurements_vicon,  timestamps_op
	  .. output - measurements_vicon, timestamps_op (same size), timestamps_vicon
	
	*generate files (graphs \ merged graphs \ correlation).
	  .. input - measurements_vicon, measurements_op, timestamps_op
	  .. output - graph files (...(

